debreate (0.7.12-dev6-2) xenial; urgency=high

  * Add Russian Gettext translation
    Use GitHub URL the check for updates
    Add mimetype info & icons for system "Open with..."
    Removed some old code for version information
    Fixed opening projects from command line
    Cleaned up code
    Removed some unused & deprecated modules & classes
    Added fixed & updated modules from unstable branch
    Added maintainer scripts postinst & prerm
    Use new about dialog
    Use custom hyperlink controls
    Use os.chmod module in build rather than system chmod command
    Import some modules from 'unstable' branch
    Fix first run window not closing
    Fixes for wx 3.0 compatibility
    Fixed Quick Build
    Added arm64 to archituctures
    Optionally use custom filename for menu launcher
    Fix problems with add/remove/delete in dependency list
    Option to enable/disable tooltips (wx 3.0 only)
    Install packages after build with gdebi
    Replace some selection controls with check boxes
    Show which required fields are empty in build dialog
    Fix cancelling progress dialogs
    Progress dialogs optionally show task count
    Menu option to open logs directory
    Add manpage
    Use 'man debreate' output for 'debreate --help' option
    - Uses default manpath if installed, otherwise uses directory man/man1

